        <updateDate>2020-02-03T19:40:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Black Lung Benefits Disability Trust Fund Solvency Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill extends until December 31, 2030, the excise tax on coal from U.S. mines. This tax is a source of funding for the Black Lung Disability Trust Fund. </p>]]></text>
